      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "@MichaelBorgwardt The API level is the <code>Arrays.fill</code> method declaration, how it is implemented is unspecified. A JVM could special case the method without using JNI. For example, <code>Math.cos</code> may look like a StrictMath JNI call in JDK sources, but most JVMs replace the Java method with an intrinsic."
