    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Yet another approach by using lambda above java 8</p>\n\n<pre><code> Arrays.stream(new Integer[nodelist.size()]).map(e -&gt; \n Integer.MAX_VALUE).toArray(Integer[]::new);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 11782782,
      "reputation" : 19,
      "user_id" : 8621690,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/831b310e7456740247175d02d4e3c87c?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Ansh Srivastava",
